commentPostTextItems.html: Well a resounding victory for South Africa, one that makes them winners, the first time for them, of this VB Series
Jonty Rhodes gets the man of the match award for his 61 not out off 68 balls
Shane Bond gets the man of the series award for his 21 wickets in the tournament
The South Africans are handed their winners medallions at the presentation
And following the conclusion of the presentation some fireworks go off
